	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Looks correct. <br /><br />Just note that the direct page addressing modes wrap within the same page. So the effective address range will be 0000H-00FFH / 0100H-01FFH depending on the direct page flag.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


